1b:T432,Internal evidence clearly identifies MERIZELLE as an oxidized regenerated cellulose (ORC) absorbable hemostat for surgical bleeding control, categorized under Endo Surgery division. This is a well-established class of topical hemostatic agents. The product description and classification are consistent. However, brand attribution is missing (manufacturer listed as Meril Life Sciences but brand field empty), no external verification sources available, no SKU examples, and no source files. The entity type is confirmed as product_family (a complete hemostatic agent product line). Semantic meaning is clinically clear - ORC hemostats are standard surgical consumables that absorb blood and promote clotting, then dissolve over time. Division indicates endoscopic/minimally invasive focus but ORC hemostats are used broadly. Confidence set to 0.75 due to lack of external verification and missing brand information. Recommend review to: 1) confirm brand ownership, 2) verify product is actively marketed, 3) obtain additional product specifications or formats if available.17:["$","$L1a",null,{"product":{"product_name":"MERIZELLE - Oxidized Regenerated Cellulose Hemostat","product_name_display":"MERIZELLE - Oxidized Regenerated Cellulose Hemostat","sku_code":"MRL-HEM-001","product_family":"MERIZELLE - Oxidized Regenerated Cellulose Hemostat","product_family_display":"MERIZELLE - Oxidized Regenerated Cellulose Hemostat","slug":"merizelle---oxidized-regenerated-cellulose-hemostat","images":[{"id":"444b3d244dc3","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c4b442ffa53c7211ead57b/cover_b730b114.jpg","original_filename":"cover_merizelle_1665144119pdf_5e0ca6a9c1.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":335206,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:59:00.484818+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":1654,"height":2339},{"id":"31dc07998d8f","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c4b442ffa53c7211ead57b/cover_0f6e1fae.jpg","original_filename":"cover_merizelle_1665144119pdf_5e0ca6a9c1.pdf.j